<h3><p align="center">HELLO! I am Anushik and welcome to Notbook Notbuk!


What started out as a favourite past-time for me turned out to be my bread and butter now and I wouldn’t have expected it to come this far 5 years ago.

I always had the penchant for stationeries particularly notebooks and would always wonder how nice it would be to have them the way I wanted and this sparked my curiosity about the ins and outs of notebooks. That was the beginning of everything!

Notbook-Notbuk started out in September 2010 while I was working my day job as a graphic designer. It started out as an online handmade business and slowly made way to bazaars and stores. As sales started picking up, I realized that I had a difficult time coping hence my decision to focus on the business. What drives me on in this endeavour is the overwhelming support I get from all the lovely people around me – family & friends and not forgeting, all the loyal customers. I am especially thrilled and overjoyed (still am!) when I see people using a product of “Notbook-Notbuk”. It truly makes all the hard work and effort worthwhile!</h3>
